OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775426988
OL,3,CCouncillor's warning as dog's 'mauled
OL,4,Cto death' on walk with five-month-old
OL,5,Cbaby
OL,7,FAn Oxfordshire councillor has issued a
OL,8,Fwarning to members of the public after
OL,9,Fhis dog was "mauled to death" during a
OL,10,Fwalk on Good Friday.
OL,12,FCherwell District Councillor, Eddie
OL,13,FReeves said his dog Coco, a cavapoo
OL,14,Fwas attacked while walking in Banbury.
OL,16,FThe incident happened on West Bar
OL,17,FStreet on Friday morning. (3 April)
OL,19,FCllr Reeves is warning families with a
OL,20,Fbaby or a small dog to stay "well
OL,21,Faway."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
