PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775426988
OL,3,CCouncillor's warning as dog's 'mauled
OL,4,Cto death' on walk with five-month-old
OL,5,Cbaby
OL,7,FPosting on Facebook he said: "Our
OL,8,Fdarling cavapoo, Coco, has just been
OL,9,Fmauled to death while walking in town
OL,10,Fwith our five-month old baby.
OL,12,F"It happened in an instant.
OL,14,F"There is blood all over me and our
OL,15,Fbaby, neither of whom were bitten.
OL,17,F"Thames Valley Police are on their
OL,18,Fway, but the number of young men with
OL,19,Fdangerous dogs in this country is out
OL,20,Fof control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
