OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775426988
OL,3,CCouncillor's warning as dog's 'mauled
OL,4,Cto death' on walk with five-month-old
OL,5,Cbaby
OL,7,F"The dogs need to be put down."
OL,9,FReacting to Cllr Reeves' post, the MP
OL,10,Ffor Banbury, Sean Woodcock said: "This
OL,11,Fis really awful Eddie.
OL,13,F"I'm so sorry to read this. "My
OL,14,Fcondolences to you and your family."
OL,16,FMeanwhile Cllr Andrew Crichton added:
OL,17,F"Eddie, I am so sorry to read this.
OL,18,FAbsolutely disgusting that this has
OL,19,Fhappened. May Coco rest in peace.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
